### 🗄️ 3. Prisma Schema

```prisma
model User {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  email     String   @unique
  name      String?
  image     String?
  credits   Int      @default(10)
  plan      String   @default("free")
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  jobs      Job[]
  txs       CreditTransaction[]
  accounts  Account[]
  sessions  Session[]
}

model Job {
  id         String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId     String
  user       User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  feature    String   ← "fashion", "product", "creative"
  prompt     String
  inputUrls  String[] ← Mảng URL ảnh input
  outputUrl  String?
  quality    String   @default("sd")
  status     String   @default("pending") ← pending/processing/done/failed
  credits    Int      @default(1)
  createdAt  DateTime @default(now())
}

model CreditTransaction {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId    String
  user      User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  amount    Int
  type      String   ← "purchase", "usage", "bonus"
  stripeId  String?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}
```

---

### ⚙️ 4. API Route: `/api/generate`

```typescript
// Nhận request từ Frontend, proxy lên chainhub, trừ credits
POST /api/generate
Body: FormData { feature, image, image_2?, quality, orientation }

Flow:
1. Verify user session (NextAuth)
2. Kiểm tra credits đủ không
3. Gửi FormData lên chainhub.tech/images/edits
4. Lưu Job vào DB + trừ credits
5. Trả về outputUrl cho frontend
```

---

### 🎨 5. Prompt Templates (Hard-coded)

Mỗi tính năng có 1 prompt mặc định, user không cần gõ:

```typescript
export const FEATURE_PROMPTS = {
  swap_clothing: "Replace the shirt in image 2 with the shirt in image 1...",
  swap_background: "Replace the scene in image 1 with the scene in image 2...",
  swap_face: "Replace the face in image 1 with the face in image 2...",
  change_color: "The color of the outfit in the photo turns red...",
  to_anime: "Transform photos into anime style",
  restore_photo: "Restore this old photo into a clean, high-quality...",
  // ...
}
```

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `pnpm build` — kiểm tra không có TypeScript errors
- `pnpm lint` — kiểm tra code quality

### Manual
1. Chạy `pnpm dev` → mở `http://localhost:3000`
2. Đăng nhập bằng Google (NextAuth)
3. Thử upload 2 ảnh vào tính năng "Thay áo"
4. Bấm Generate → kiểm tra ảnh output trả về đúng
5. Kiểm tra credits bị trừ trong DB
